cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CVPR

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with depth estimation from stereo images and proposes a method to increase accuracy and reduce computational complexity. 
2. cs.RO (Robotics) is also likely as the paper mentions using ego-motion to transform the disparity map of the previous frame into the current frame. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possible category as the paper mentions using a Kalman filter for prediction and updating the disparity map. 
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper proposes a method to improve the accuracy of depth estimation. 
5. cs.CVPR (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is a possible category as the paper deals with computer vision and proposes a method to improve the accuracy of depth estimation.
